                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">15. General Provisions</h2>

                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#92600a] mb-2">15.1 Entire Agreement</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    These Terms, together with our <a href="/privacy" class="text-[#92600a] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>, constitute the entire agreement between you and RavencoreX LLC regarding the use of the App.
